If you have any problem when you use this skill, you can contact us with email : chenying24@lenovo.com

You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off the device. 
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you device- just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show. 
After connecting Alexa to your Lenovo Link Pro products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Lenovo Link Pro" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Lenovo Link Pro account in our "Lenovo Link Pro" app;
(3). You need to have some Lenovo Link Pro devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our “Lenovo Link Pro" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Lenovo Link Pro" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Open your “Lenovo Link Pro” app——Me——More Services
(8). Then click on “Alexa” icon and link to Amazon “Alexa” follow the steps , you'll be redirect to the success page
(9). Now all setup is finished. 
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:

“Alexa, turn on light"
“Alexa, turn off light"
